Revision history for Perl extension Log::Channel

0.5   12 Aug 2002
	- Added Log::Channel::Config, bumped to 0.6; test suite
	- Configuration should apply to new channels created
	later, and should handle hierarchy correctly.

0.5   12 Jul 2002
	- cleaned up internal configuration data structure
	- merged 'package' and 'topic' into single 'topic'
	- don't create duplicate channels for same topic
	- more tests
	- decoration format string like log4j
	- commandeering of carp/croak should apply to all subpackages

0.4   28 Jan 2002
	- added 'commandeer' function
	- consolidated internal data structures

0.3   22 Jan 2002
	- created.
